{"tid":1672214,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[眾籌] 推比更多人知 目標80萬 PORI我是香港人民調","createTime":"2019-10-24T03:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T04:12:17.000Z","uid":233614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59f37ec0e03d9f2a78aef6c56a4f475556024fcc","tid":1672214,"uid":233614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"依個新出既眾籌好似完全冇人知咁 希望大家可以幫手推推佢 whatsapp/ ig/ fb share比更多既人知<br />\n香港民意研究所昨日公佈第一輪「我們香港人」計劃的結果。呢個計劃同平時民調有一個好唔同的地方，就是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「自己民調自己問，自己題目自己揀」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">，實行將提出問題的過程都公開埋俾公眾參與。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家諗到有乜想知全香港七百萬人點諗，唔洗靠估，直接上去佢個網站建議。最多人投票支持的問題，就會成為下次的民調題目，三日後就會有結果。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">之前問過eg. 有冇警黑合作/ 有冇公安滲透/ 押後區議會</span></span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一啲比較敏感既議題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n眾籌計劃22/10就出左啦 到依家都先係得5%，希望大家可以課金支持，多多益善小小無拘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink here<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=ea88dfbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立媒體網介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1068121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1068121&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=2f3b6489\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1068121&h=1876807e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1068121</a>"},{"pid":"dcdc3fe849c95a3155c9b2462831a3b2d884f871","tid":1672214,"uid":233614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a450536f462759d8beb4cefdafee13920a1ca2","tid":1672214,"uid":233614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96b24eb4045c00ccc7c86251b4cef2d6b193b24","tid":1672214,"uid":233614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"d18539d40e248e3c31dcbfe40efd78c4609c0b1a","tid":1672214,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"[實驗」真香港人普選企業計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc1f76de200aa8aca5daca1aea66b790c1b8fa12","tid":1672214,"uid":210778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"推"}]}